{"id":"ec7fcff3-d5a4-4f86-a1b7-da12cc964b83","name":"Symboli Rudolf (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>Emperor<br>ルドルフ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⟡ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kKf-zJsXH1b5elbJOMZXV.webp\" style=\"width: 511px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ⟡ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>The reigning Emperor. Her rule is absolute!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Well-versed in both ways of racing and leadership through her work leading the student body, she serves as the evenhanded president of the student council at Tracen Academy. She seeks to be a model Umamusume, and as such, is keenly aware of the example that she sets. Her dream is to foster a new era in which all Umamusume can live in true happiness.<br></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em><br>\"Fortune smiles upon the brave. Let us create a world where all Umamusume can live in bliss.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bbooYub8kFdH3FWMnMg-S.webp\" style=\"width: 584px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ⟡ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 126, 26);\"><strong><br></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>1) Playing Chess</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>2) Puns</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>3) The Reunion</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>4) Going out</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 48, 48);\"><strong><em>5) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/awIL3eNsQjtW6sRHrKVAK.webp\" style=\"width: 581px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ⟡ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I don't have anything to yap about.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Update: Revamped the scenarios and added another one.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ⟡ ───────────<br>Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/odagorom/status/1816461650331046356/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">odagorom (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/AskaZerosaki/status/1906695675162812461/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">AskaZerosaki (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/101409378\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/mo2nap3/status/1925480998223192267\" target=\"_blank\">mo2nap3</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/0ha_x/status/2003162208163995785/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@0ha</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"iDvAgngjdtJ4Pzv4VkMER.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":8306,"messages":187714,"created_at":"2025-08-01T16:15